Subject: Secunia Research: UltimateZip unacev2.dll Buffer Overflow
	Vulnerability


====================================================================== 

                    Secunia Research 11/05/2006

      - UltimateZip unacev2.dll Buffer Overflow Vulnerability -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

Affected Software....................................................1
Severity.............................................................2
Description of Vulnerability.........................................3
Solution.............................................................4
Time Table...........................................................5
Credits..............................................................6
